name: C/CSS - Green Silk Satin
description:
These pieces have all been designed from original drawings which have then been photographed with and later manipulated using various Apps on an i-phone.

The resulting image is then printed on to a silk satin fabric and measures approxiamatly 18 x 160 cm after finishing. 

Landed price includes P&P costs anywhere in the world.

Pieces can be ordered directly from James Donald by using the Paypal service below.

For trade orders there is a minimum order of 6 pieces please quote code “C/CSS - Green“ when asking for costings.

Additional images can be found at http://www.pickone.co.uk/green.html
